Sophie Cookson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sophie_Cookson 0 Sophie Louise Cookson (born 15 May 1990) is an English actress best known for portraying secret agent Roxanne "Roxy" Morton / Lancelot in the 2014 spy film Kingsman: The Secret Service and its 2017 sequel The Golden Circle.
